## Rule

- Prefer copying or adapting from these sources over writing net-new components.
- For all shadcn work (add/fix/style/compose/CLI **and** choosing a component), read **`agent-os/skills/shadcn/SKILL.md`** and follow its workflow, Critical Rules, and "Project rules — core-fe" section.
- When in doubt which component to use: on first build pick the single best and implement; if the user wants options, present best 3 with direct links and ask.
- If you need a detail (e.g. "sidebar with icons only"), ask the user.
